  "prompt": "Where do you get the best cakes in pune?",
  "response": "Pune has a vibrant culinary scene, especially when it comes to desserts and cakes. Here are some popular places known for their delicious cakes:\n\n1. **Chitale Bandhu Mithaiwale** - Renowned for its traditional sweets, they also offer a variety of cakes that are popular among locals.\n\n2. **German Bakery** - Famous for its delectable cakes and baked goods, this location is a must-visit for cake lovers.\n\n3. **Pancakes & Waffles** - This caf\u00e9 offers a range of sweet treats, including delicious cakes and pastries.\n\n4. **Sweet Stuff** - Known for their innovative flavors and custom cakes, Sweet Stuff is a favorite for both birthdays and special occasions.\n\n5. **Theobroma** - A popular bakery chain, they serve a variety of cakes, including rich chocolate cakes and cheesecakes.\n\n6. **Hunt for Cake** - Known for its customized cakes, they offer a wide selection for birthdays, weddings, and other celebrations.\n\n7. **The Flour Works** - They have a fantastic selection of gourmet cakes along with a cozy caf\u00e9 atmosphere.\n\n8. **Dolcetto by Gelato** - Offers a range of pastries and cakes, including options for those with dietary restrictions.\n\n9. **Baker Street** - Popular for their freshly baked cakes, Baker Street is a go-to place for cake enthusiasts.\n\nEach of these places has its unique offerings, so it might be worth trying a few to find your personal favorite!",
